%html
  %head
    %meta{:content => "text/html; charset=UTF-8", "http-equiv" => "Content-Type"}/
    %meta{:charset => "utf-8"}/
    %meta{:content => "width=device-width, initial-scale=1", :name => "viewport"}/
    :css
      *{
      padding: 0px;
      margin: 0px;
      }
  %body
    .wrapper{style: "padding: 30px 0px; font-family:arial"}
      %table{style: "margin: 0 auto;max-width: 677px;width: 100%; font-family:arial;margin-top: 50px;padding: 12px 12px;"}
        %tbody
          %tr
            %td{style: "font-weight: 700;"}
              Promotional Code For You
          %tr
            %td{style: "margin-top: 22px; float: left; line-height: 25px; font-size: 15px;"}
              A promotional code shared by
              = "#{@order.user}."
          %tr
            %td{style: "margin-top: 22px; float: left; line-height: 25px; font-size: 15px;"}
              #{@user_name} recently signed up to GradReady and has given away their promotional code to you. When you sign up to Gradready and use this discount code not only will you get a 10% discount on your purchase but your friend will also get a little bit of money back as well. To redeem your code, as you go to pay for your course make sure to use the discount code #{@order.generated_promo.token} or use this link:
          %tr
            %td{style: "margin-top: 22px; float: left; line-height: 25px;font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 60px;"}
              = link_to user_promo_link_url(@order.generated_promo.token), user_promo_link_url(@order.generated_promo.token), style: "color: #007833; text-decoration: underline; font-style: italic; font-weight: 700;"
          %tr
            %td{style: "margin-bottom: 24px; float: left;font-size: 15px;"}
              Kind regards,
          %tr
            %td{style: "margin-bottom: 34px; float: left;font-size: 15px;"}
              GradReady Student Success Team

